{"tid":1852284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為防中國新型肺炎　俄羅斯關閉遠東地區邊境","createTime":"2020-01-30T11:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T11:24:17.000Z","uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d225369d71e2ceedac39154316c482a2fae89243","tid":1852284,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:11:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505709-20200130.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505709-20200130.htm&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=514cc90f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505709-20200130.htm&h=ca802ec3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505709-20200130.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯至今並無新型肺炎確診個案，為防範新型冠狀病毒，即日起關閉遠東地區邊境，並暫停中國國民的電子簽證。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯昨日已採取多項措施，防範疫情傳入，包括關閉與中國接壤邊境的陸路交通，直至3月1日；來往俄國和中國的火車服務暫停，只餘一條由莫斯科到北京的火車線仍然行駛；又會在未來幾日內決定是否暫停俄中兩國之間的航空交通。另外，又要求在農曆新年假期回國的中國留學生，在3月1日之前不要返回俄羅斯的大學上課。"},{"pid":"3d7ecaaa95c79a4d3a144ea63573a37c24e72895","tid":1852284,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"關撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562862adaaf9def86d727ef935d9dd8860af8c3e","tid":1852284,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:23:06.000Z","msg":"(真攬炒聯署)要求美國禁止中国和香港人入境美國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/prohibit-chinese-and-hk-people-entry-united-states-until-end-wuhan-coronavirus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fprohibit-chinese-and-hk-people-entry-united-states-until-end-wuhan-coronavirus&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=1a8f1c1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/prohibit-chinese-and-hk-people-entry-united-states-until-end-wuhan-coronavirus</a><br />\n大家快簽, 攬炒聯署"},{"pid":"d842832c4be041388185468965994f2fb3e3ca8d","tid":1852284,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}